snippet.title: Pirates! Gold gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Pirates! Gold, Dos PC game produced by Microprose in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/pirates-gold/576/
Playing as a pirate in the Carribean of 17th century. Plundering villages and having epic battles.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
